{"tid":1003843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國貴族學院44歲女教師　被控在教室與17歲學生做愛","createTime":"2019-02-01T03:55:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T04:45:22.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c3086dd99ae00e15271c5ed3b4e7a3ca9f8a4fd2","tid":1003843,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T03:55:19.000Z","msg":"美國又傳女性教師與自己學生做愛的不倫事件。<br />\n<br />\n44歲女子拉希莉(Aniyta Lahiri)原本是佛蒙特州知名寄宿學校林頓學院(Lyndon)的教師，警方獲報，去年春季拉希莉至少與自己班上一名17歲男學生做愛兩次，其中一次是在拉希莉住處，另一次則是在學校教室中。拉希莉日前遭到逮捕，校方並且立刻將她解雇。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，這名男學生去年夏天已經從學校畢業，之後主動找上警方，檢舉拉希莉與他的不倫關係，男學生表示，2人是先透過社群網站開始「交往」，進而發生性行為。已婚的拉希莉有2個孩子，雖已遭到學校解雇，仍對外否認自己與男學生間的不倫行為。<br />\n<br />\n林頓學院是佛蒙特州知名的貴族寄宿學校，一年學費高達台幣130萬元，校長裴瑞(Twiladawn Perry)強調，將全力配合警方調查。（於慶中／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"11f47a335dfd3973113ff1fa5e9844d6fabebb15","tid":1003843,"uid":122,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T03:55:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.whoateallthepies.tv/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/suarez-chelsea.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.whoateallthepies.tv%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2012%2F11%2Fsuarez-chelsea.gif&h=ed56b048&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1920eee85052f9f10b3c8ef050807a43a94899eb","tid":1003843,"uid":62822,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T03:55:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9c2e6c817641b99f46c0934c0c2e8ae2733ce59","tid":1003843,"uid":156913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1920eee85052f9f10b3c8ef050807a43a94899eb","tid":1003843,"uid":62822,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T03:55:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T03:56:55.000Z","msg":"唔等啦， 44 歲鬼婆， 不了"},{"pid":"92a360e47514f6cb2e8f07da7f6bb3adfca37ac9","tid":1003843,"uid":60057,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T03:57:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190131/640_cd3a9ab029d0ca282814c67a7ae66ca8.j